        public void replaceExtendedResourceContainer(ExtendedResourceContainer oldC,
                                             ExtendedResourceContainer newC)
        Replaces an existing Extended Resource Container within the model with a new one. All the Linking Resources related to the old Extended Resource Container are updated and linked to the new Extended Resource Container.
        Parameters:
        oldC - is the existing Extended Resource Container to replace.
        newC - is the new Extended Resource Container.
